This project focuses on predicting product sales using Machine Learning techniques. The objective is to build a regression model that estimates sales based on advertising expenditures across different platforms such as TV, Radio, and Newspaper.

Sales prediction helps businesses make data-driven decisions by understanding how marketing investments impact revenue. This project demonstrates a complete machine learning workflow from data preprocessing to model evaluation.


